# SwiftPM — vendored local packages (TV Safari)

## Required app dependencies

- Do **not** rely on **`XCRemoteSwiftPackageReference`** alone for packages the **TV Safari** target **must** link (e.g. **`Zip`**) unless the team accepts **network / cache / CI** resolution risk.
- **Zip** must live at **`Packages/Zip`** with a valid **`Package.swift`**, and **`project.pbxproj`** must use **`XCLocalSwiftPackageReference`** with **`relativePath = "Packages/Zip"`** and **`XCSwiftPackageProductDependency`** **`productName = Zip`**.

## Anti-patterns

- Re-adding **`https://github.com/marmelroy/Zip`** as the **only** source without vendoring — restores *Missing package product `Zip`* when resolution fails.
- Stale **`Package.resolved`** pins pointing at a **remote** Zip after the project switched to **local** — can confuse Xcode until reset or file is updated.

